result.name: Yifengtang

reviews.text:
Have one vegetarian option, delicious. Restaurant is clean, tidy and comfortable. Not very crowded.

Staff are nice and helpful. They are local and Japanese staff.

Next time will try another instead of corn.

Price is a little bit expensive but still acceptable with the good quality and location.

Highly recommended.
Ramen broth is tasty perhaps it’s due in part to msg. Dumplings are very tiny. Service is prompt and friendly.

Today I tried their new 200gram pork ramen. The soup base is good and tasty, the ramen is rather soft. And there re three types of pork- grill pork, boiled pork and sliced semi fatty pork.. the quantity of meat is massive ! However , the pork itself is not so tender, only the sliced fatty pork taste slightly better without too hard and tough. But my friend try the mini size of the typical ramen is pretty good, it is rich in flavor . Next time might better pick the original version
The service is great , but the food is not consistent.
Here is the famous ramen restaurant in Japan,and I ate Kuro ramen as special.I think here is as same as the taste in Japan.Great.

這裡點餐要掃碼自助。沒有問題，可以減輕侍應的負擔吧。
要瓶裝的啤酒都沒有，沒有問題，就要生啤吧，都知道一人喝不完兩杯。
週末就是要在吃前飲啖啤酒，可是偏偏在拉麵上桌很久也不見來。侍應愛理不理，避你眼神而過。
很懷念以前有位日本人女侍應的時候...那叫日本式的貼心服務。
對不起，如果以前有四星的話，現在只能減半。
我相信半年內不會來這家一風堂。
（圖：姍姍來遲的啤酒。看不到的還有那差勁的服務）
平過一蘭，淡過一蘭，湯太少又唔俾添加，塊肉好薄

result.name: Silvercord

reviews.text: Well equipped mall at the center of the shopping district. Have affordable shops as supposed to all the designer brands near by. Good places to eat inside, also affordable.

Silvercord is a shopping mall and office complex at the heart of Canton Road in Tsimshatsui. Its location is very convenient with walking bridge connected to the Harbour City, the largest shopping mall in Hong Kong. However, the mall seems a bit outdated in the interior decoration and the mall design. Always use liked a stepping stone to the nearest Harbour City from my point of view.

The concierge is really friendly always smiling and super helpful, he knows what service means, he took the pain to help me and not just by pointing in a vague direction, while welcoming me, and i felt like a guest in the building rather than an annoyance!!! Keep it up management you're doing great to have such awesome staff!!
Genki Sushi is the best addition to this mall
Good quality products. Attractive.
